		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">灵嗣利用巨尾进行至多2段的横扫攻击，均造成<span color="#7fbfff">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="511" width="438" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">灵嗣操控巨尾，抛出3枚水泡，水泡落地造成<span color="#7fbfff">30%</span><span>伤害并继续向前弹跳2次，随后消失。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="799" width="398" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">灵嗣抬起前身向前跺下，造成<span color="#7fbfff">70%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">灵嗣将尾部掷向地面，造成<span color="#7fbfff">80%</span><span>伤害；「晦隐」状态下还会产生一枚水泡，落地造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">30%</span><span>伤害，弹起2次后消失。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="511" width="424" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">灵嗣转身翻越，进入「<span textDecoration="underline">晦隐</span><span>」状态，该状态下灵嗣施放技能前后都会闪现，并且全抗提升，解除对</span><span color="#7fbfff">水元素</span><span>的免疫。<br/>不处于「晦隐」状态下持续附着</span><span color="#7fbfff">水元素</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="799" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">灵嗣背对玩家用后肢猛踢，造成<span color="#7fbfff">70%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/涌流%B7霜夜灵嗣.assets/Image_28.png')" x="64" y="64" blendMode="normal">
