			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">晦隐：抗打断0，全抗性提升<span color="#ffccbf">60%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffccbf">120%</span><span>，允许受到水元素伤害；充能条总量</span><span color="#7fbfff">100</span><span>/</span><span color="#7fbfff">150</span><span>(深渊)，受到</span><span color="#7fbfff">水元素</span><span>攻击后根据水元素的量积攒</span><span color="#7fbfff">20n</span><span>或</span><span color="#7fbfff">3</span><span>，受到月反应伤害积攒</span><span color="#7fbfff">3</span><span>，充满退出状态。</span></p>
			</content>
